				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-8-C%E1%BB%91-h%E1%BB%AFu-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%E1%BB%91c-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/poem-OMzIcEXGWASbO9P2feqjhw">Bát ai thi kỳ 8 - Cố hữu bộc xạ tướng quốc Trương Cửu Linh - 八哀詩其七－故右僕射相國張公九齡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/B%E1%BB%91-V%E1%BB%87-ki%E1%BB%81u-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-PBnBAw5mcime8MMuBM3u9A">Bố Vệ kiều hoài cổ - 布衛橋懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/Chi%E1%BA%BFm-l%C4%A9nh-Nam-Kinh/poem-CRDohRP4Laa0RzuoQ0dFhg">Chiếm lĩnh Nam Kinh - 占領南京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/author-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-D%E1%BB%B1/Co-T%C3%B4-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-HeD57fPg5knj9eW9c-k8Cw">Co Tô hoài cổ - 姑蘇懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-D%E1%BB%B1/author-LNsZKHBxiNPYPCsZsRmHhg">Lương Hữu Dự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/H%C3%A1n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u/poem-PJaD8IBtGb89DRPhQs0r5w">Hán Dương vãn diểu - 漢陽晚眺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-%C4%90%E1%BB%89nh-T%C6%B0/%C3%94-giang-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-iTI_aoWrqZL_KOUcC2AxIw">Ô giang hoài cổ - 烏江懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-%C4%90%E1%BB%89nh-T%C6%B0/author-beZBZ33RQejrn17600j3Gg">Cung Đỉnh Tư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%E1%BB%9F-B%C3%A1-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-m%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-TPlLwwuYJSJE-HXakmdHLg">Sở Bá Vương mộ kỳ 1 - 楚霸王墓其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Tr%E1%BA%A5n-H%E1%BA%A3i-l%C3%A2u-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Duy-K%C3%ADnh-t%C3%A1c/poem-xoWfzmZsGHOG8Ykmvg5tvA">Trấn Hải lâu đồng Duy Kính tác - 鎮海樓同惟敬作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-rCWfEQnyNck8EX0Qq8YKLQ">Âu Đại Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Gia-H%E1%BB%B1u/T%E1%BB%B1-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ch%C3%A2u-ho%C3%A0i-Giang-%C3%82m-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-azZ8b-HicLtnyhuSWmxxgw">Tự Thường Châu hoài Giang Âm đồ trung tác - 自常州懷江陰途中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Gia-H%E1%BB%B1u/author-6zYzZx8bQhzm8Wdeftq7Wg">Lý Gia Hựu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-thi-T%E1%BA%BF-y%C3%AAu-cung/poem-IBdFC2KKY3sTcInpqURGXA">Vịnh sử thi - Tế yêu cung - 詠史詩－細腰宮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-QGyhycNQKN2UVF9H-N6Zaw">Hồ Tằng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
